Subject: [VB] Installing nose sheet metal.

>3. Should I find a spot welder on ebay? rather than using a mig welder? I
>need to fill in the drilled out spot welds too.

A spot welder will not fill drilled holes, better to mig ( or braze ) and grind.
Some mig welders have a spot / stitch capacity, and some can have it
added later, check with the tool manufacturer.
Dave\X/


